        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/3ab097/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-01-05T08:35:15.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I had the 14 Montmains and wrote this:</p>\n<p>On pnp, no reduction. Citrus, acid, alcohol tame, clean, slight sour bite. A lovely wine drinking well now with clear potential. QPR and a rebuy. I am looking forward to trying others from this producer.</p>",
